# Smart clc


🧮 Smart Calculator

A Smart Calculator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, enhanced with API integration for advanced calculations.

✨ Features

➕ Perform basic arithmetic (add, subtract, multiply, divide)

🧠 Handle complex expressions with API-powered calculations

🎨 Simple and responsive UI

⚡ Fast and accurate results

🎯 Learning Highlights

This project helped me practice:

🔗 API integration in JavaScript

⏳ Handling asynchronous operations with fetch()

🎨 Building an interactive and user-friendly UI
